    - document eval EXPR gotcha

2.50  Mon May 19 17:39:22 2008

    - add support for INTEGER, FLOAT, NUMBER and STRING
        - added scalar.t
    - updated documentation

2.43  Thu May 15 21:14:08 2008

    - fix @isa bug
        - added t/isa.t
    - scope cleanup
